jei_desc.chaosawakens.defossilizer:
Used to turn Fossilized Mobs into Spawn Eggs.

It requires an Aluminum Power Chip as well as a specific liquid depending on the fossil.
jei_desc.chaosawakens.copper_defossilize: The Copper Defossilizer can only defossilize Stone and Gravel fossils..
jei_desc.chaosawakens.iron_defossilizer: The Iron Defossilizer can defossilize any fossils (except the crystal ones), but takes 4 times longer than the Copper Defossilizer.
jei_desc.chaosawakens.crystal_defossiliz: The Crystal Defossilizer can defossilize any non-stone fossils, taking as long as an Iron Defossilizer to do so.
